latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Saying goodbye is sometimes a part of life. but we can say it’s the toughest part of life that we can’t even say proper goodbye at that time But our memories will always speak for our true relationship wherever we go. these time it’s even toughest just like the first time i said goodbye to you. these months we travelled alot. we suffered from good things and bad things together , but the main point is we suffered ‘together’. but now i’m gonna suffer everything alone without you and also you are gonna do same thing. i’ll miss the all moments we shared together, that ‘mean’ look you everytime give me when i asked you for anything , that ‘jati reje’ word i used say you and in return ‘jau j chhu thoda time ma’ ; ‘jato rahis to radta pan nai avde’ , i’ll miss everything , every fight , every emotions we shared together. you always disturbed me and always pull my legs by your innovative minds. you are more thn elder brother to me , My Best Friend ❤️The memories will always stay with me. i’ll always thanks to god for sending you. Thank you so much BHAI for always being with me and for always love me like you do. I love you so much Vicky Dada❤️ @vishwas19 

ps: i know thodu vadhare thai gayu 😒🤢 but bolvu pade su kari sakie 🤕👺and also don’t forget to watch end 😂😂

latestIgtvVideos.title: Fake Accounts 🙏🏻
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Instagram, Facebook, Twitter are all kinds of fascinating places on the internet, where one can scrutinize new people. Social networking sites are utilized to share information about who you are with the rest of the world, which is excellent.
However, social media retains its downside.
Creating a fake identity using social networks is becoming trendy in today’s society. Many people decide to make a profile with untrue personal information about them to meet a significant other, attain their desire to be someone they are not, and for the satisfaction of a new start. 
This is not related to any boy or girl. And this is not for all boys. This is about why we can not support each other?
Why are we snatching them down by doing this kind of action?
And we are already facing issues due to COVID-19. We all are passes through tough times. Let's spread peace and success around us. That's all. Thank you, everyone, for the support.🙏🏻🤍
